	abstract = {Effective communication is essential for academic success, but traditional grading systems often suffer from delayed feedback, inconsistency, and high manual workload. To address these challenges, this paper introduces 'WriteEdge' a web-based platform that leverages Generative AI with optimized prompt engineering to provide personalized feedback on written communication. Preliminary results demonstrate a functional system integrated with Gemini 2.5 Flash to provide responsive feedback, dashboards, and AIgraded reports. This web-based platform includes modules with student and admin portals which have practice modules, and test assessment modules and personalized AI generated feedback reports. Future scope of WriteEdge includes customization for institutional rubrics, AI-bot for doubt resolution, and voice-based test assessments. Our work highlights the potential of GenAI with prompt-engineered modules to transform learning and grading communicationbased content both written and verbal which will reduce instructor workload and provide students with detailed insights to help them smoothly transition from academia to professional careers.  © 2026 IEEE.},
